{"tid":655161,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"就係你班正宗毒撚搞咁多垃圾手機驚","createTime":"2018-05-06T09:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T08:27:49.000Z","uid":8307,"like":36,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b4de494196f2498bfa211463aa512eb32dbf2311","tid":655161,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"真係好撚嬲呀,我開始玩手機驚唔算早,由10年前開始玩<br />\n雖然到而家都穩定有好驚,但就一大堆倒模同垃圾充斥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心就唔好浪費app store個位啦,浪費網絡資源,知唔知非洲啲小朋友幾多冇得上網<br />\n<br />\n課金呢一樣野又係好撚ON9既,咁撚商業既詞都掛係嘴邊係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至從出左啲轉蛋驚,究竟出現左幾多個倒模<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n故事設計描寫都省番<br />\n你地班ON9正宗毒撚又真係受架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家商業化手機驚真係簡單啦,是但係熱門驚到抄個玩法出黎就係一隻驚<br />\n當然呢一個唔單係玩法既問題,<br />\n連劇情都要倒模,得罪講句,你同CCTVB有撚分別咩<br />\n性無能男主角 開後宮 全世界唯一一個XXOO 偽正義台詞 爆SEED<br />\n而後宮入面通常 傲嬌一個 大小姐一個 眼鏡一個 青梅竹馬一個......咩女都加啲咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁都算啦,起碼都算有劇情呀<br />\n最近仲出左D：我擺明係無劇情架啦,我擺明係好撚商業架啦,我擺明係個個角色同玩法都經過熱門驚心挑選架啦,你吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢又唔撚係走休閒路線架喎,玩法又無咩架喎,但佢就係生存到,仲大收fuck <br />\n我就廢事點名啦,即係fgo個D囉<br />\n<br />\n好簡單,我對而家手機驚不滿既就係 玩法倒模 劇情倒模 人設都開始有少少倒模 廢萌 商業化<br />\n仲有係咁認老婆班ON9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係毒撚到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 現實一定毒撚到核爆<br />\n你講邊個邊個係你老婆,你唔會覺得好柒架咩?<br />\n我覺得連登唔應該歡迎咁低智既人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我夠膽講 老婆前老婆後個D 成日口邊掛住咩課金咩課金個D 以為自己講得出課好多金好勁個D<br />\n全部都係腦殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cf1d928139c247897423be7037c72068a4ff4a","tid":655161,"uid":94167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:35:47.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"84b17f13fbf9eafe9c95fcd5ee6cc73e9fc3f324","tid":655161,"uid":80323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"玩足10年手機game又覺得垃圾都唔玩家用機同pc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedae60d1bf67f317ea7c03209be9c30cb224ee0","tid":655161,"uid":177388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"所以玩FGO"},{"pid":"725f072148acf1ba9837b2ea03cfe285806d5900","tid":655161,"uid":8307,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"84b17f13fbf9eafe9c95fcd5ee6cc73e9fc3f324","tid":655161,"uid":80323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"玩足10年手機game又覺得垃圾都唔玩家用機同pc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:44:50.000Z","msg":"on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話自己食左幾十年飯,係咪幾十年期間唔食得其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045f187ba0deab6c1261d9853e23354ff7ed7633","tid":655161,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"睇嚟樓主先係垃圾，10年前就開始玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：一直玩開pc/ps4 電話game狗也不屌"},{"pid":"5b804af3ac9b02034bcada90fe94f0eae7e1945f","tid":655161,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"045f187ba0deab6c1261d9853e23354ff7ed7633","tid":655161,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"睇嚟樓主先係垃圾，10年前就開始玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n